<?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?>
<knowl mode="exercise" xmlns="https://spatext.clontz.org" version="0.2">
    <intro>
        <p>Let <m>A</m> be <em>any</em> <m>4 \times 4</m> matrix.</p>
    </intro>
    <!-- {{#tasks}} -->
    <knowl>
        <content>
            <p>
Give a <m>4 \times 4</m> matrix <m>{{name}}</m> that may be used to
perform the row operation <m>{{row_op}}</m>.
            </p>
        </content>
        <outtro>
            <p><m>{{name}}={{mat}}</m></p>
        </outtro>
    </knowl>
    <!-- {{/tasks}} -->
    <knowl>
        <content>
            <p>
Use matrix multiplication to express the matrix obtained by 
first applying <m>{{first_op}}</m>, then <m>{{second_op}}</m>,
and finally <m>{{third_op}}</m> to <m>A</m> (note the order).
            </p>
        </content>
        <outtro>
            <p>
                <m>{{matrix_product}}A</m>
            </p>
        </outtro>
    </knowl>
</knowl>
